title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Evening' game
title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Evening' game
maintext:
DES MOINES, Iowa (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening’s drawing of the Iowa Lottery’s “Pick 3 Evening” game were:
7-6-8
(seven, six, eight)
